Ce spune?

00:42:27.560 --> 00:42:29.120
Te doare spatele?

00:42:29.320 --> 00:42:31.200
Tot timpul?

00:42:31.401 --> 00:42:34.720
- Întotdeauna?
- Uneori nu, alteori simt dureri.

00:42:34.920 --> 00:42:37.440
Deci, aproape tot timpul.

00:42:37.640 --> 00:42:41.560
